query:
SELECT 
            namespace_name as "namespace_name: Vec<String>",
            n.warehouse_id,
            n.protected,
            namespace_properties as "properties: Json<Option<HashMap<String, String>>>",
            n.updated_at
        FROM namespace n
        INNER JOIN warehouse w ON w.warehouse_id = $1
        WHERE n.warehouse_id = $1 AND n.namespace_id = $2
        AND w.status = 'active'
